meta.description: This mod adds tips to loading menus. It also allows for modpacks and mods to add their own tips!
meta.long_description:
This mod will display useful tips on certain game screens such as the world loading screen. The tip shown will be cycled out every five seconds. The pool of tips can be expanded by resource packs, other mods, and even modpacks. You can learn more about configuring the tips here.
